data.description: Immaculately maintained and move-in ready corner lot home offers a perfect blend of modern elegance and timeless charm. This 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem boasts a spacious backyard, perfect for enjoying sunsets from your lanai or while relaxing in your living room. The open-concept living area with a gourmet kitchen, Granite counter tops, kitchen Island measuring 09X04 is ideal for entertaining. Plus, you'll appreciate the low HOA fees and no CDD fees, making it an affordable choice for first-time buyers or any buyer. Located in a desirable neighborhood with top-rated schools and easy access to highways, this home is also conveniently near shopping, dining, and public transportation. Don't miss out on this opportunity; schedule a showing today! Homes like this don't stay on the market for longâ€”act now!
